--- META ---
name: array exact match
summary: Test exact array matching with equals - order matters
tags: [array, matching]
owner: team/gripmock
links:
  - https://github.com/bavix/gripmock/issues/840

// Test: Exact array match - order matters: ips: ["10.64.0.1", "10.64.0.2"]
// See Issue #840: https://github.com/bavix/gripmock/issues/840

--- ENDPOINT ---
inventory.InventoryService/GetResourceDecorationByIPsStream

--- REQUEST ---
{
  "ips": [
    "10.64.0.1",
    "10.64.0.2"
  ],
  "k8s_cluster_id": "scale-test-cluster"
}

--- RESPONSE ---
{
  "ips_to_decorations": {
    "10.64.0.1": {
      "decoration": "web-frontend",
      "environment": "production"
    },
    "10.64.0.2": {
      "decoration": "api-backend",
      "environment": "staging"
    }
  }
}
